msgid ""
"All MOE models supported by vLLM-Ascend. But we have only verified the "
"performance on deepseek-v3.1/r1 models."
msgstr "vLLM-Ascend支持的所有MOE模型。但我们仅在deepseek-v3.1/r1模型上验证了性能。"

