#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md
msgid "DefaultEplb"
msgstr "DefaultEplb"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md
msgid ""
"Open-source EPLB algorithm. Adds redundant experts to the hottest, packs via"
" balanced assignment with local constraint exchange."
msgstr "开源EPLB算法。向最热的专家添加冗余，通过带局部约束交换的均衡分配进行打包。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md
msgid "`2`"
msgstr "`2`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md
msgid "SwiftBalanceEplb"
msgstr "SwiftBalanceEplb"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md
msgid ""
"Optimized for low-bandwidth environments. Supports intra-node and inter-node"
" expert redundancy, joint optimization of expert placement. "
"**(Recommended)**"
msgstr "针对低带宽环境优化。支持节点内和节点间专家冗余，联合优化专家放置。**（推荐）**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md
msgid "`3`"
msgstr "`3`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md
msgid "FlashLB"
msgstr "FlashLB"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md
msgid ""
"Statistical method using sliding-window mean/variance/covariance of expert "
"loads. Uses FlashTree layered search for optimal replica allocation and "
"`minimize_redeploy` for incremental adjustment. Best for high-frequency load"
" fluctuations."
msgstr ""
"统计方法，使用专家负载的滑动窗口均值/方差/协方差。使用FlashTree分层搜索进行最优副本分配，使用`minimize_redeploy`进行增量调整。最适合高频负载波动场景。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md:99
msgid "Static EPLB"
msgstr "静态EPLB"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md:101
msgid "Initial Setup (Record Expert Map)"
msgstr "初始设置（记录专家映射）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md:103
msgid ""
"We need to add environment variable `export EXPERT_MAP_RECORD=\"true\"` to "
"record expert map. Generate the initial expert distribution map using "
"expert_map_record_path. This creates a baseline configuration for future "
"deployments."
msgstr ""
"需要添加环境变量`export "
"EXPERT_MAP_RECORD=\"true\"`以记录专家映射。使用expert_map_record_path生成初始专家分布映射。这将为未来部署创建基线配置。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md:117
msgid "Subsequent Deployments (Use Recorded Map)"
msgstr "后续部署（使用已记录映射）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md:119
msgid ""
"Load the pre-recorded expert map for consistent performance. This avoids "
"recalculating distributions at runtime."
msgstr "加载预记录的专家映射以获得一致的性能。这避免了在运行时重新计算分布。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md:130
msgid "Critical Considerations"
msgstr "关键注意事项"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md:132
msgid "Parameter Tuning:"
msgstr "参数调优："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md:133
msgid ""
"expert_heat_collection_interval: Higher values (e.g., 600+) for stable "
"workloads; lower values (e.g., 50-100) for fluctuating traffic."
msgstr ""
"expert_heat_collection_interval：稳定工作负载使用较大值（如600+）；波动流量使用较小值（如50-100）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md:134
msgid ""
"algorithm_execution_interval: Should be ≥ 50 to avoid premature balancing "
"during startup."
msgstr "algorithm_execution_interval：应≥50，以避免启动期间过早均衡。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md:135
msgid ""
"num_redundant_experts: Must match (num_experts + num_redundant_experts) is "
"divisible by expert-parallel size."
msgstr ""
"num_redundant_experts：必须满足(num_experts + num_redundant_experts)能被专家并行度整除。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md:137
msgid "Hardware Requirements:"
msgstr "硬件要求："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md:138
msgid ""
"Ensure that all NPUs have identical memory capacity and compute "
"capabilities."
msgstr "确保所有NPU具有相同的内存容量和计算能力。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md:139
msgid ""
"Network bandwidth must support expert redistribution traffic (≥ 10 Gbps "
"recommended)."
msgstr "网络带宽必须支持专家重分配流量（建议≥10 Gbps）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md:141
msgid "Monitoring & Validation:"
msgstr "监控与验证："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md:142
msgid ""
"Track metrics: Search for [Expert Hotness] in log, we will calculate the "
"peak-to-average ratio of the load for each layer at different ranks, and "
"then find their mean and maximum values. Current means actual peak-to-"
"average ratio, update means estimated peak-to-average ratio after algorithm "
"adjustment."
msgstr ""
"跟踪指标：在日志中搜索[Expert "
"Hotness]，我们将计算不同rank上每层负载的峰值均值比，然后找出其平均值和最大值。Current表示实际峰值均值比，update表示算法调整后的预估峰值均值比。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md:143
msgid "Use vLLM monitor to detect imbalances during runtime."
msgstr "使用vLLM监控器在运行时检测负载不均衡。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/expert_parallelism_load_balancer.md:144
msgid ""
"Always verify expert map JSON structure before loading (validate with jq or "
"similar tools)."
msgstr "加载前务必验证专家映射JSON结构（使用jq或类似工具进行验证）。"

msgid "# Expert Parallelism Load Balancer (EPLB)"
msgstr ""

msgid "## Overview"
msgstr ""

msgid "## EPLB Effects"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"- Reduced Latency: Dynamically balances expert loads to minimize TTFT and TPOT by distributing workloads evenly across experts.\n"
"- Adaptive Scaling: Automatically adjusts to workload fluctuations while maintaining stable performance."
msgstr ""

msgid "## Support Scenarios"
msgstr ""

msgid "### Models"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"All MOE models supported by vLLM-Ascend.\n"
"But we have only verified the performance on deepseek-v3.1/r1 models."
msgstr ""

msgid "### MOE QuantType"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"| QuantType                       | Supported Hardware          |\n"
"| ------------------------------- | --------------------------- |\n"
"| W8A8 / W8A8-Dynamic             | A2, A3 |\n"
"| W4A8 (with fused MC2 enabled)   | A2, A3 |\n"
"| MXFP4                           | Ascend 950 Products         |\n"
"| MXFP8                           | Ascend 950 Products         |"
msgstr ""

msgid "## How to Use EPLB"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"| Mode | Config in `eplb_config` | Env Variable |\n"
"| ---- | ----------------------- | ------------ |\n"
"| **Dynamic EPLB** | `dynamic_eplb: true` | `DYNAMIC_EPLB=true` |\n"
"| **Recording** (generate expert map) | `expert_map_record_path` | `DYNAMIC_EPLB=true` or `EXPERT_MAP_RECORD=true` |\n"
"| **Static EPLB** (load pre-recorded map) | `expert_map_path` | none required |"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"> [!IMPORTANT]\n"
"> For Dynamic EPLB and Recording modes, the env variable acts as a safety guard: setting `dynamic_eplb: true` in config alone is not enough — the assertion requires `DYNAMIC_EPLB=true` or `EXPERT_MAP_RECORD=true`. Static EPLB (loading a pre-recorded map via `expert_map_path`) does **not** require an env variable."
msgstr ""

msgid "### Dynamic EPLB"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"| Parameter | Description | Default |\n"
"| --- | --- | --- |\n"
"| dynamic_eplb | Enable dynamic EPLB. | False |\n"
"| expert_heat_collection_interval | Interval for collecting expert heat. | 600 |\n"
"| algorithm_execution_interval | Interval for executing the balancing algorithm. | 50 |\n"
"| eplb_policy_type | EPLB policy type. | 2 |\n"
"| num_redundant_experts | Number of redundant experts. | 0 |"
msgstr ""

msgid "#### EPLB Policy Types"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"| Value | Policy | Description |\n"
"|-------|--------|-------------|\n"
"| `0` | Random | Randomly swaps experts between ranks. Suitable for basic testing only. |\n"
"| `1` | DefaultEplb | Open-source EPLB algorithm. Adds redundant experts to the hottest, packs via balanced assignment with local constraint exchange. |\n"
"| `2` | SwiftBalanceEplb | Optimized for low-bandwidth environments. Supports intra-node and inter-node expert redundancy, joint optimization of expert placement. **(Recommended)** |\n"
"| `3` | FlashLB | Statistical method using sliding-window mean/variance/covariance of expert loads. Uses FlashTree layered search for optimal replica allocation and `minimize_redeploy` for incremental adjustment. Best for high-frequency load fluctuations. |"
msgstr ""

